# ==============================================================================
# KEEP THESE FILES - Essential for package functionality
# ==============================================================================

# These files are explicitly included via package.json "files" field:
# - dist/**/* (compiled JavaScript and type definitions)
# - lib/**/* (library exports for programmatic usage)  
# - bin/**/* (CLI executables)
# - config/*.sample.yaml (configuration templates)
# - docs/API.md (API documentation)
# - docs/ARCHITECTURE.md (architecture documentation)
# - docs/DEPLOYMENT.md (deployment guide)
# - README.md (main documentation)
# - LICENSE (license file)
# - CHANGELOG.md (version history)
# - SECURITY.md (security policy)

# ==============================================================================
# PLATFORM SPECIFIC - Exclude platform-specific files
# ==============================================================================

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon?

# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Linux
*~
.fuse_hidden*
.directory
.Trash-*

# ==============================================================================
# FINAL PACKAGE SIZE OPTIMIZATION
# ==============================================================================

# The goal is to keep the published package under 25MB with all essential files
# Package contents should include:
# - Compiled JavaScript (dist/)
# - Library exports (lib/) 
# - CLI tools (bin/)
# - Essential documentation (README, API docs, etc.)
# - Configuration templates
# - Type definitions
#
# Everything else is excluded to optimize download and installation speed